<div class="title">
<div class="quote-controls"></div>
<img loading="lazy" alt="" width="24" height="24" src="https://www.chiefdelphi.com/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/r/ce7236/48.png" class="avatar"> RoyalKnight:</div>
<blockquote>
<p>Thank you so much! I kind of realized this as well but I’m</p>
